{"id":88505,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2010/08/卫报图说：中国洪灾-2/","date":"2010-08-03T22:21:11Z","modified":"2010-08-03T22:21:11Z","title":"卫报图说：中国洪灾","content":"<p><img src=\"http://static.guim.co.uk/sys-images/Guardian/Pix/pictures/2010/7/22/1279792997761/A-street-lamp-is-partiall-007.jpg\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" /><br />\n泛滥的长江水几乎将重庆的街灯淹没。（美联社）</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://static.guim.co.uk/sys-images/Guardian/Pix/pictures/2010/7/22/1279792992451/A-man-stands-in-flood-wat-002.jpg\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" /><br />\n在湖北省武汉市，街上两辆公交车相遇，红车左侧，一名路人经过。（法新社/ Getty Images）</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://static.guim.co.uk/sys-images/Guardian/Pix/pictures/2010/7/22/1279792993649/A-man-struggles-as-he-wad-003.jpg\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" /><br />\n在辽宁省铁岭市，一名男子跋涉过被洪水淹没的农田。（Yao Jianfeng/ 美联社）</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://static.guim.co.uk/sys-images/Guardian/Pix/pictures/2010/7/22/1279792995733/A-resident-fills-a-bucket-005.jpg\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" /><br />\n一名东流镇的居民从泛滥的长江中打了一桶水，远处一艘船经过。（Aly Song/ 路透社）</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://static.guim.co.uk/sys-images/Guardian/Pix/pictures/2010/7/22/1279792990800/People-wade-through-mud-t-001.jpg\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" /><br />\n在重庆，淌过泥水，人们前往长江和嘉陵江交汇处的河岸。（Peter Parks/ 法新社/ Getty Images）</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://static.guim.co.uk/sys-images/Guardian/Pix/pictures/2010/7/22/1279795114271/A-resident-walks-through--012.jpg\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" /><br />\n四川渠县，一名居民走过因为洪水而被垃圾阻塞的街道。（路透社）</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://static.guim.co.uk/sys-images/Guardian/Pix/pictures/2010/7/22/1279796464022/A-boy-swims-in-the-floode-017.jpg\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" /><br />\n重庆，一名男孩儿在长江中游泳。（Peter Parks/ 法新社/ Getty Images）</p>\n<p><span><img src=\"http://static.guim.co.uk/sys-images/Guardian/Pix/pictures/2010/7/22/1279794989999/Lightning-strikes-in-Poya-010.jpg\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" /><br />\n</span>九江鄱阳县，闪电撕裂了天空。（Aly Song/ 路透社）</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://static.guim.co.uk/sys-images/Guardian/Pix/pictures/2010/7/22/1279794988848/A-child-sleeps-on-a-couch-009.jpg\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" /><br />\n重庆被洪水淹没的街上，男孩在沙发上睡着了。（Shi Tou/ 路透社）</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://static.guim.co.uk/sys-images/Guardian/Pix/pictures/2010/7/22/1279795116689/Residents-enjoy-the-water-014.jpg\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" /><br />\n在湖北武汉市被洪水淹没的河堤上，居民们暂时享受着流水。（美联社）</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://static.guim.co.uk/sys-images/Guardian/Pix/pictures/2010/7/22/1279795209964/A-dog-swims-at-a-park-flo-016.jpg\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" /><br />\n武汉市一座被长江水淹没的公园里，一只狗游过镜头前。（路透社）</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://static.guim.co.uk/sys-images/Guardian/Pix/pictures/2010/7/22/1279795115530/Rescuers-reinforce-the-ba-013.jpg\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" /><br />\n九江鄱阳县，武警们在加固洪涝区域的河堤。（Aly Song/ 路透社）</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://static.guim.co.uk/sys-images/Guardian/Pix/pictures/2010/7/22/1279794987730/Residents-walk-across-a-b-008.jpg\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" /><br />\n江西省鄱阳县，人们走过洪水淹没的桥。（Aly Song/ 路透社）</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://static.guim.co.uk/sys-images/Guardian/Pix/pictures/2010/7/22/1279792996784/A-resident-rows-a-boat-on-006.jpg\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" /><br />\n东流镇，一名居民划船经过大水淹没的街道。（Aly Song/ 路透社）</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://www1.feedsky.com/t1/395535317/dongxinet/feedsky/s.gif?r=http://item.feedsky.com/~feedsky/dongxinet/~8172838/395535317/6276617/1/item.html\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" width=\"0\" height=\"0\" /></p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www1.feedsky.com/r/l/feedsky/dongxinet/395535317/art01.html\"><img src=\"http://www1.feedsky.com/r/i/feedsky/dongxinet/395535317/art01.gif\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" /></a></p>\n<p>请看原文：<br />\n<a title=\"卫报图说：中国洪灾\" href=\"http://item.feedsky.com/~feedsky/dongxinet/~8172838/395535317/6276617/1/item.html\" target=\"_blank\">卫报图说：中国洪灾</a></p>\n","author":176,"categories":[20534],"tags":[9727,10607]}